channel.title: ASF JIRA
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HADOOP-18438] AliyunOSS: AliyunOSSFileSystemStore deleteObjects interface won't return the objects that failed to delete
item.description: AliyunOSSFileSystemStore deleteObjects interface used "simple mode" to do batch delete, which  won't return the objects that failed to delete. So, all the failed objects won't be real deleted in the following retries.
item.summary: AliyunOSS: AliyunOSSFileSystemStore deleteObjects interface won't return the objects that failed to delete

status.description: The issue is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.
